{"tid":602734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅致光：派4000元未有詳細時間表 (15:22)","createTime":"2018-03-23T07:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T07:47:34.000Z","uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3eb565cb9fcc3af18d5c35ffe63bf15afdc5dff7","tid":602734,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:36:49.000Z","msg":"財政司長陳茂波與勞福局長羅致光今午見記者，公布向低收入或無收入人士，一筆過發放4000元現金津貼。陳茂波指，計劃需要招聘人手和有行政開支，稍後到立法會申請撥款時，將會交代具體細節。羅致光說，希望在下一個財政預算年度前，完成發放有關金額，但暫未能提供詳細時間表。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波指，預算案公布後，他聽到社會聲音而有所反思，同意關愛共享部分的覆蓋面可更廣。陳表示，是次計劃是有條件的，認為仍屬於針對性和聚焦的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光說，由於申請人數將以百萬計，需要增聘人手和電腦系統處理，希望在下一個財政預算年度前，完成發放有關金額，「要和時間競爭」，但今日暫未能提供時間表，會稍後交代。"},{"pid":"0d22958ff23e5aa10e4b070cedd3b9dcc2cc0ae5","tid":602734,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0b62358778db7b88c499f6487937cf271346f2","tid":602734,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:39:14.000Z","msg":"上次6k 今次4k<br />\n<br />\n劏房波會計出身, 益下會計班人<br />\n2k 去左admin 成本度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n垃圾 廢柴 落台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de8732aa9e2c3773b4e74dba16b0935f00b4f0a","tid":602734,"uid":10165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d22958ff23e5aa10e4b070cedd3b9dcc2cc0ae5","tid":602734,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"